  ],
  "technicalDetails": "MOBI is based on the Palm Database (PDB) format. The PDB header at offset 0 contains a 32-byte book name. At offset 60-67 are the type ('BOOK') and creator ('MOBI') fields that identify the format. Record 0 contains the PalmDOC header followed by the MOBI header and optional EXTH metadata block with author, publisher, and ASIN fields.",
  "completenessScore": 85
}



